# Cursor Rules for Tracking Speed Reading

## Code Style
- Use English for all code, comments, and variable names
- Use Vietnamese for user-facing text and UI elements
- Follow React best practices and functional components
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling
- Implement responsive design for mobile and desktop

## Component Structure
- Keep components focused and single-purpose
- Implement proper error handling
- Use motion animations for smooth user experience where helpful

## File Organization
- Keep related components in the components folder
- Use descriptive file names
- Maintain consistent import/export patterns

## Performance
- Minimize bundle size
- Use proper caching strategies where appropriate
